objects.description: [Uroburos](https://attack.mitre.org/software/S0022) can store configuration information in the Registry including the initialization vector and AES key needed to find and decrypt other [Uroburos](https://attack.mitre.org/software/S0022) components.(Citation: Joint Cybersecurity Advisory AA23-129A Snake Malware May 2023)
